[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/45/62/456208.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1453549","time":"2019-6-13 13:33","userId":"sukaretto","userName":"czy0729","userSign":"(安卓/iOS Bgm App http://bgm.tv/group/topic/350677 ...)","message":"不应该是那基本黄色的标准日本语吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/65.gif\" smileid=\"104\" alt=\"(bgm88)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1454231","time":"2019-6-15 20:35","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"+1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/82/408266.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1453560","time":"2019-6-13 14:00","userId":"lyc326662175","userName":"LyC","userSign":"","message":"感觉自学不靠谱…还是得报班学…","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/23/2331.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1454157","time":"2019-6-15 15:01","userId":"leins","userName":"leins=pallange","userSign":"","message":"+1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/45/18/451822.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1453562","time":"2019-6-13 14:32","userId":"muzzle","userName":"Muzzle","userSign":"(最孤独最强)","message":"插眼","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/43/11/431197.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1453566","time":"2019-6-13 15:14","userId":"cts","userName":"影约","userSign":"(不只用眼睛，更用脑袋看动画。)","message":"新编日语教程。用标日过了N1后连假名都写不好的人一堆堆。入门后你想用什么学就用什么学没区别的。对比国内日语专业用的教材难度大概是综合日语≥新编日语（或者基础日语）≥新标日≥新编日语教程≥其他杂七杂八的自称能马上就学会日语的教材。时间的话，说不准，能力考很水，有高手两星期过N1，也有菜鸡读了四年大学过不了N2。你只需要计算自己的学习积极性在记住6000个单词和200个语法的时间，一般能轻松过。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/47/56/475611.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1453978","time":"2019-6-14 23:04","userId":"475611","userName":"想翻身的咸鱼君","userSign":"","message":"感谢"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#5-2","id":"1454060","time":"2019-6-15 08:39","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"","message":"6000单词和200语法就是标日书里的嘛"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/68/26866.jpg","floor":"#5-3","id":"1454239","time":"2019-6-15 21:02","userId":"hc","userName":"月火","userSign":"","message":"N1连假名都写不好 +1"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/43/11/431197.jpg","floor":"#5-4","id":"1454575","time":"2019-6-16 21:21","userId":"cts","userName":"影约","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">東瀬まつり太</span> 说: 6000单词和200语法就是标日书里的嘛</q></div>查了一下书，课标里面应该是540个语法N2，741个语法N1。6900个单词N2，10100个单词N1。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/78/267845.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1453568","time":"2019-6-13 15:18","userId":"basertyu","userName":"小鸠世界第一可爱","userSign":"(noblesse oblige)","message":"<a href=\"https://www.jlpt.jp/samples/sample09.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://www.jlpt.jp/samples/sample09.html</a><br>直接选个难度做套模拟试试呗，只是追求合格不难的，先给自己心里有个数<br>合格判定：<br><a href=\"https://www.jlpt.jp/guideline/results.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://www.jlpt.jp/guideline/results.html</a><br>n1、n2一共有三大项，词汇+语法，阅读，听力，每项满分60分，总共180分。<br>单项至少19分，总分至少100分即合格。<br>*评分机制不是按题算分，而是按正答人数占比算分，建议每个大项正答率稳定70%以上<br><br>如果经常看动画片的话，听力、词汇会轻松一些，阅读稍微吃力，语法是难点（个人感想）<br>不过不太推荐考n2，没什么用，n1才算是学习日语的开始，要报考JLPT的话建议多多准备直接n1<br>然后，我没有教材，教材就是看了6年冻鳗，还有玩了1年多日服手游<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">当然这不是应试手段，不建议学习……","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/47/56/475611.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1453976","time":"2019-6-14 23:04","userId":"475611","userName":"想翻身的咸鱼君","userSign":"","message":"感谢"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/50/315025.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1453932","time":"2019-6-14 20:30","userId":"kasper4649","userName":"张某某的哥特","userSign":"(ただの人間。)","message":"标日，请","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/47/56/475611.jpg","floor":"#7-1","id":"1453977","time":"2019-6-14 23:04","userId":"475611","userName":"想翻身的咸鱼君","userSign":"","message":"感谢"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/47/4759.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1454045","time":"2019-6-15 05:23","userId":"boday","userName":"boday","userSign":"(猫も棒から落ちる)","message":"我对新标日（新编标准日本语）唯一的不满是它自己另立了一套日语语法体系，和其他地方广泛使用的日语语法名词不太对得上，初学者可能会因此困惑。<br><br>另外个人经历来说，纯自学的话，刚入门时容易自己脑补和忽略一些基本知识和概念，有别人带一带的话可能会少走点弯路，不过也不是必需……入门之后（差不多 N4）如 #5 所说，随便怎么折腾吧。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/45/25/452531.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1454054","time":"2019-6-15 07:55","userId":"piglalala","userName":"piglalala","userSign":"(如果能被美少女包养该多好啊)","message":"人教标日吧","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/23/2331.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1454156","time":"2019-6-15 15:00","userId":"leins","userName":"leins=pallange","userSign":"(この身はそなたの“剣”──そう誓ったはずだ。 ... . ...)","message":"入门请找人教或者报班 有些发音语调入门读不对听不对 对以后影响不小","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/63/266388.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1454211","time":"2019-6-15 19:27","userId":"266388","userName":"恋花绽放樱飞时","userSign":"(www~)","message":"想学的专业点就新编，正常的话黄皮标日就行了","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/47/56/475611.jpg","floor":"#11-1","id":"1454499","time":"2019-6-16 17:31","userId":"475611","userName":"想翻身的咸鱼君","userSign":"","message":"感谢"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/36/363649.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1454215","time":"2019-6-15 19:43","userId":"abrin","userName":"送你一朵秋野花","userSign":"","message":"黄油+查词","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/60/346025.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1454614","time":"2019-6-17 00:16","userId":"346025","userName":"BWsmoke","userSign":"(685728819，这是一个全新的黄油群，欢迎各位加入 ... ...)","message":"我记得frontwing的官中可以显示上下两排，一排中文一排日文，你可以试试","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/15/97/159769.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1454674","time":"2019-6-17 09:20","userId":"srvenx","userName":"東雲閑","userSign":"(必须成为天野远子的作家。)","message":"红宝书和蓝宝书，这两本，一起买大概要80多。<br>日语专业机油给我的倾情推荐~","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/47/56/475611.jpg","floor":"#14-1","id":"1455496","time":"2019-6-19 18:53","userId":"475611","userName":"想翻身